Ni Xi shrugs and picks up her camera, taking several photos of the monsters she's certain are dead. Then, she pulls out her favorite dagger—the exquisite Death Dagger—and begins to cut one of the monster's horns. She then moves on to cut the other. However, as soon as Ni Xi finishes cutting, the monsters suddenly start to catch fire and quickly turn into ashes. The horns she cut also turn into ashes.
"Well... this does have its pros and cons..." Ni Xi sighs. "At least I still have the photos."
